title: Natasha Oakley flaunts sizzling bikini body and washboard abs in leopard-print high waisted-bikini
text:
She's the jaw-dropping bikini blogger who never puts a foot out of line when it comes to fashion.

And Natasha Oakley certainly didn't disappoint on Friday, as she flaunted her incredible physique in a stunning leopard-print bikini on Bondi BeachSydney.

The sizzling 29-year-old - who, according to sources is recently single - looked nothing short of sensational as she flaunted her famous curves by the ocean.

Bringing the heat! Sizzling model Natasha Oakley (pictured) sauntered along Bondi beach in a leopard-print bikini on Friday

The A Bikini A Day blogger exhumed confidence in the high-waisted two-piece, which emphasised her ample assets to perfection.

The slinky number also showed off her washboard abs and slender pins, while Tash sported a pair of oversized sunglasses to shield her face from the sun.

The blonde bombshell left her hair naturally wavy for the occasion, before placing a straw hat on her head as she basked in the spring sunlight.

What a figure! Natasha flashed her very pert derrière in the skimpy bikini

Flashing the flesh! The confidence 29-year-old looked nothing short of sensational in the high-waisted two-piece, which emphasised her ample assets to perfection

Blonde bombshell: Natasha left her hair naturally wavy for the occasion, before placing a straw hat on her head as she basked in the sunlight

According to sources, Tash is now newly single after splitting from boyfriend Theo Chambers.

Daily Mail Australia have contacted a representative for Natasha for comment.

The pair had confirmed their romance on New Years Eve last year.

In January, they had even sparked engagement rumours in Los Angeles in January, when Natasha wore a ring during a romantic date.

Sultry stunner! Natasha then lay own in the summer sunlight, where she laughed and smiled with a mystery pal

Taking a break! Tash couldn't help but smile as she was entertained by a pal during the red hot outing

Months earlier in July, Natasha had confirmed her split from French model and father-of-one Gilles Souteyrand after three years together.

'Yes, I am single at the moment,' she wrote on Instagram in response to a follower who asked about her relationship status.

Before dating Gilles, she was romantically linked to French Big Brother star Martin Medus.
